name: Balluff BES0510- Inductive Full-Metal Sensors, Range 4 mm, PNP (NO)
leaf_category: Inductive Full-Metal Sensors, Range 4 mm, PNP (NO)
description: The resilient stainless steel BES inductive full-metal sensors have been specifically developed for applications in harsh environments. The housing and sensor front are manufactured from stainless steel. The robust active surface is resistant to impacts, mechanical stresses, and abrasive media. We offer additional variants with PTFE and ceramic coating against welding spatter. The extreme resilience of our sensors can reduce your maintenance costs,thus increasing the availability of your system.
